'''Aqua'''是一棟位於[[美國|美國]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[洛普區|洛普區]]的住宅辦公混用摩天大樓，共82層，<ref name=022807ChicagoTribune>{{cite news| first=Susan| last=Diesenhouse| title=Work to begin on Aqua tower| url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2007-02-28/business/0702280163_1_starwood-hotels-hotel-rooms-resorts-worldwide| work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]| date=28 February 2007| accessdate=2014-12-18| archive-date=2014-12-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219004014/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2007-02-28/business/0702280163_1_starwood-hotels-hotel-rooms-resorts-worldwide| dead-url=no}}</ref>以及地下1層為停車場。大廈1樓到8樓建築面積為13,000平方公尺（140,000平方英尺），8樓露臺面積7,669平方公尺（82,550平方英尺），露臺設有花園、觀景亭、游泳池、熱水浴池、步道、以及觀景火坑。8樓以上的建築面積每一層大約是1,500平方公尺（16,000平方英尺）。<ref name=CTBUH>{{cite web| title=Aqua Tower Tour| publisher=[[CTBUH|CTBUH]]| url=http://www.ctbuh.org/Events/ToursVisits/2008TourArchive/AquaTowerTour/tabid/779/language/en-GB/Default.aspx| date=17 December 2008| accessdate=2014-12-18| archive-date=2014-12-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219011450/http://www.ctbuh.org/Events/ToursVisits/2008TourArchive/AquaTowerTour/tabid/779/language/en-GB/Default.aspx| dead-url=no}}</ref>Aqua大廈在2009年[[安波利斯摩天大樓獎|安波利斯摩天大樓獎]]獲得第一名<ref name=Lutz>{{cite news| first=BJ| last=Lutz| title=Aqua Named 2009 Skyscraper of the Year| url=http://www.nbcchicago.com/around-town/real-estate/aqua-chicago-skyscraper-award-84988917.html| work={{link-en|NBC Chicago News|WMAQ-TV}}| date=24 September 2010| accessdate=2013-02-10| archive-date=2010-02-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100227031345/http://www.nbcchicago.com/around-town/real-estate/aqua-chicago-skyscraper-award-84988917.html| dead-url=no}}</ref> ，並在2010年入圍{{link-en|國際高層建築大獎|International Highrise Award}}。<ref>{{cite press release| url=http://www.international-highrise-award.com/downloads/2010/101105IHA_Pressrelease_AwardCeremony.pdf| title="The Met" High-rise apartment building wins International Highrise Award 2010| date=2010-11-14| quote=Commendation certificates were awarded to the 262-meter high-rise apartment building Aqua Tower (Chicago) by Studio Gang (Chicago)…| publisher=[[German_Architecture_Museum|German Architecture Museum]]| accessdate=2014-12-18| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219011954/http://www.international-highrise-award.com/downloads/2010/101105IHA_Pressrelease_AwardCeremony.pdf| archivedate=2014-12-19| df=}}</ref>

==建築師==
