Aqua建築設計師為{{link-en|珍妮·甘建築事務所|Studio Gang Architects}}（Studio Gang Architects, SGA）創辦人{{link-en|珍妮·甘|Jeanne Gang}}（Jeanne Gang），這是甘的首次設計案<ref name=King>{{cite news |first=John |last=King |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2006/10/10/DDG40LKPJQ1.DTL&hw=Millennium+Park+Chicago&sn=006&sc=219 |title=Visionary architect fuses imagination, common sense |date=10 October 2006 |work=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]] |accessdate=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2013-07-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HvX6ao2O?url=http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Visionary-architect-fuses-imagination-common-2550190.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且是首位由女性建築師所設計最高的摩天大樓。<ref name=Becker>{{cite news| title=The Third School| url=http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/the-third-school/Content?oid=921989| date=4 May 2006| work={{link-en|Chicago Reader|Chicago Reader}}| last=Becker| first=Lynn| accessdate=2014-12-18| archive-date=2014-10-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027024204/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/the-third-school/Content?oid=921989| dead-url=no}}</ref>記錄建築師為魯文貝格建築事務所（Loewenberg & Associates）的詹姆士·魯文貝格（James Loewenberg）領導的團隊。<ref name=Novak>{{cite web| first=Lawrence| last=Novak| title=Case Studies: Concrete Mixed Use Buildings: Aqua Tower, Chicago, Illinois| url=http://www.cement.org/buildings/buildings_mixed_aqua.asp| publisher=Portland Cement Association| date=2010| accessdate=10 February 2013| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213000000/http://www.cement.org/buildings/buildings_mixed_aqua.asp| archivedate=2012年2月13日}}</ref>

==設計==
Aqua令人注目的特點在於其外觀設計，在陽台設計上，每個陽台平均向外延伸3.7公尺（12英尺）。<ref>{{cite news| title=Architecture Jobs Metro News| url=http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.metronewsdetails&rn=997246239| work=World Architecture News| date=10 February 2008| accessdate=2014-12-18| archive-date=2014-11-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141126194323/http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.metronewsdetails&rn=997246239| dead-url=no}}</ref>為了創造富有雕刻性的立面，在設計上利用不規則弧形陽台的組合，創造出波浪樣式的建築立面。<ref name="emporis"/><ref>{{cite journal| title=Studio Gang Architects design Aqua Tower in Chicago| url=http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.projectview&upload_id=1918| work=World Architecture News| date=5 February 2008| accessdate=2014-12-18| journal=| archive-date=2014-11-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141126194438/http://www.worldarchitecturenews.com/index.php?fuseaction=wanappln.projectview&upload_id=1918| dead-url=no}}</ref> 該設計靈感來自大湖區常見的石灰岩露頭景觀。<ref name=Sharoff>{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/04/realestate/04nati.html?ei=5088&en=358b78a841751de1&ex=1307073600&partner=rssnyt&emc=rss&pagewanted=all| work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]| title=How a Park Changed a Chicago Neighborhood| first=Robert| last=Sharoff| date=4 June 2006| accessdate=2010-04-25| archive-date=2007-09-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070902003255/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/04/realestate/04nati.html?ex=1307073600&en=358b78a841751de1&ei=5088&partner=rssnyt&emc=rss&pagewanted=all| dead-url=no}}</ref>由於波浪狀的建築立面與玻璃外牆組合，使建築立面像是波浪起伏的水面一樣，另外也因為大廈地點鄰近[[密西根湖|密西根湖]]，因此開發商麥哲倫開發有限公司（Magellan Development Group）將大廈命名為Aqua。<ref name="emporis" />

建築[[永續性|永續性]]在建築設計是重要一環之一，陽台向外延伸的設計除了美觀，也可提高遮陽限度，另外在永續性設計上也包括雨水收集系統與節能照明。建築的[[綠化屋頂|綠化屋頂]]面積也是永續性設計之一，並且是芝加哥市內，綠化屋頂面積最大的大廈。目前Aqua大廈正在受[[美國綠建築協會|美國綠建築協會]]審核LEED認證。<ref name=Stephens>{{cite journal| last=Stephens| first=Suzanne| title=Curves Over Chicago: Aqua, a new 82-story residential tower and hotel near Lake Michigan, adds a new dynamism to the city’s skyline| url=http://greensource.construction.com/green_building_projects/2010/1001_Aqua-Tower.asp| publisher={{link-en|GreenSource Magazine|GreenSource Magazine}}| accessdate=2014-12-18| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150124013904/http://greensource.construction.com/green_building_projects/2010/1001_Aqua-Tower.asp| archivedate=2015-01-24| journal=}}</ref>

Aqua大廈內包含5,100平方公尺（55,000平方英尺）的零售商圈與辦公室。1到18樓為[[酒店|酒店]]，提供215個客房。19到52樓為出租式公寓，總共475戶。53到81樓為[[分契式公寓|分契式公寓]]與[[空中別墅|空中別墅]]，共263戶。<ref name=Sharoff/>該建築是市區首座結合分契式公寓、集合式住宅、與酒店的建築。{{link-en|戰略酒店與度假公司|Strategic Hotels & Resorts}}（Strategic Hotels & Resorts）在大廈建設期間已8400萬美元合同獲得酒店經營權，但該公司因[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|環球金融危機]]影響而在2008年8月終止合同。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.hotel-online.com/News/PR2006_3rd/Sep06_AquaChicago.html |title=Strategic Hotels & Resorts, Inc. Acquiring 15 floors of the Aqua Building in Chicago for $82.4 million; Space to be Completed as 200 Hotel Rooms and 20,000 square foot Ballroom |accessdate=2014-12-18 |date=28 September 2006 |publisher=Strategic Hotels & Resorts, Inc. |work=Hotel Online |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080708212236/http://www.hotel-online.com/News/PR2006_3rd/Sep06_AquaChicago.html |archivedate=2008-07-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>{{link-en|卡爾森公司|Carlson Companies}}在2010年5月12日宣布，以1.25億美元合同獲得1到18樓酒店經營合同，並讓子公司{{link-en|麗笙酒店|Radisson Blu}}經營，這也是麗笙酒店第一個在美國的據點。<ref name=Carlson>{{cite press release| title=Carlson announces the U.S. debut of Radisson Blu with Radisson Blu Aqua Hotel, Chicago on 11.1.11| url=http://www.carlson.com/news-and-media/news-releases.do?article=4479138| date=22 September 2011| publisher=Carlson| accessdate=2014-12-18| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219013048/http://www.carlson.com/news-and-media/news-releases.do?article=4479138| archivedate=2014-12-19}}</ref>

